                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 819.55/32.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">American Chargé d’Affaires</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-11-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 15, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Chinese Government advised of contents of your November 13 through its Legation
                    in Washington. You will be informed as soon as possible of course which it
                    desires to be pursued.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
